Santon nodded as he walked up to assist Bump and Legacy, "Then we will
try to just delete the personality subroutines and leave the memories
intact." With a deft movement he activated the console that up to a
few moments ago Legacy had been using. Data began to once again scroll
across his screen.

Turning back to his console Bump also got back to work, his fingers
moving smoothly over the buttons. He was adding some code while
changing others. It would be a tricky undertaking. The screen began to
change as the coding was swiftly modified.

Looking over at Perceptor Legacy watched the ex Predacon for a long
moment before speaking, "If what you are saying is correct then what
we are attempting stands an 89.117% chance of success." His single
optic pulse once, "However if you are wrong, then what we are
attempting may meet with initial success, but there is a signifigant
chance that the original corrupted Predacon subroutines will
regenerate."
